SAY NAME1 ~Gauntlets~
SAY NAME2 ~Gauntlets of Spellweaving~
SAY DESC ~Gauntlets of Spellweaving
The Gauntlets of Spellweaving, also christened "Phalh's Roaring Success" at the moment of its creation, is an impressive artifact for a first attempt by its creator. Tailored specifically to cater to Phalh's own talents, its magical enchantments make it a valuable asset for any dabbler of both martial and magical arts, though its magic only responds to that of its creator, whether intentionally or otherwise.

STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
– Off-Hand THAC0: +4
– Spellweaving: Every melee attack increases the wearer's Casting Speed by 1 for 6 seconds.

Weight: 1~

